## Common Patterns

### Vector Math

```aria
struct Vec3 {
    x: f32,
    y: f32,
    z: f32
}

fn dot(a: Vec3, b: Vec3) -> f32 {
    return a.x * b.x + a.y * b.y + a.z * b.z;
}

fn length(v: Vec3) -> f32 {
    return sqrt(dot(v, v));
}
```

### Linear Interpolation

```aria
fn lerp(a: f32, b: f32, t: f32) -> f32 {
    return a + (b - a) * t;
}

