| Feature | `flt32` | `flt64` |
|---------|---------|---------|
| Precision | ~7 digits | ~15 digits |
| Range | ±3.4 × 10^38 | ±1.7 × 10^308 |
| Storage | 4 bytes | 8 bytes |
| Speed | Faster | Slower |
