## Immediately Invoked Function (IIFE)

```aria
// Define and call immediately
int32:result = int32(int32:x) { pass(x * x); }(5)?;  // 25

// Useful for complex initialization with local scope
Config:config = Config() {
    Config:c = Config.new()?;
    c.timeout = 30;
    c.retries = 3;
    pass(c);
}()?;
```

